<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA96">
<l>ārvallār kāṇa varaṉavaṉai yaṉpeṉṉum</l>
<l>pōrvai yataṉālē pōrttamaittuc - cīrvalla</l>
<l>tāyattā ṉāmun taṉineñci ṉuḷḷaṭaittu</l>
<l>māyattāl vaittō maṟaittu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who is able to see Hara? Effecting to cover him</l>
<l>with what is the cover called love, grace to an excellent strong</l>
<l>inheritance  we lock [him inside [our] solitary hearts</l>
<l>[and] by magic keep [him] hidden [there].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
